:\"Guard: routed === 0 ? 1 : Math.max(0, 1 - wasted / routed)\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-hs-i2-06\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"file\":\"advisor-probe.cjs\",\"line\":68,\"issue\":\"Negative scenario: rank > 5 success allows skill at rank 6 as pass; rank 5 scores 0 — boundary wrong (skill barely in top-5 should be partial failure for negative)\",\"fix\":\"Use rank > 3 for negative success, or 0.5 for rank 4-5 as marginal leak\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-hs-i2-07\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"file\":\"run-skill-benchmark.cjs\",\"line\":71,\"issue\":\"advisorMode string 'false'/'0' is truthy but not 'python' — probe skipped silently; bare --advisor-mode python not parsed correctly by _args\",\"fix\":\"Document =value requirement; add explicit string check or use strict equality for probe trigger\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-hs-i2-08\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"file\":\"build-report.cjs\",\"line\":18,\"issue\":\"d.status || 'unscored' renders '_undefined_' if status is literal string 'undefined' in JSON; == null check is correct but || fallback is loose\",\"fix\":\"Use d.status ?? 'unscored' (nullish coalescing)\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-hs-i2-09\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"file\":\"contamination-lint.cjs\",\"line\":29,\"issue\":\"trigger_phrases regex requires no blank line between key and list items; blank line silently produces zero triggers\",\"fix\":\"Document blank-line-free requirement; add warning if trigger_phrases block exists but yields no triggers\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-hs-i2-10\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"file\":\"contamination-lint.cjs\",\"line\":57,\"issue\":\"add() drops tokens with trim().length <= 2 — could miss 2-3 char skill ids like sk, py as contamination\",\"fix\":\"Lower threshold to > 1; document the false-positive avoidance rationale\"}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/review/hs/deltas/iter-002.jsonl"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/review/hs/deltas/iter-002.jsonl","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/review/hs/deltas/iter-002.jsonl","time":{"start":1780204710574,"end":1780204710580}},"id":"prt_e7c77f94c001Pigob6I2gEmhAQ","sessionID":"ses_1838ab765ffeDkoguY5zw44Q55","messageID":"msg_e7c77f220001bW4ES6C0dyvFp3"}}
